53:22.925 --> 53:24.926
- You're very kind. No, thank you.
- No, no.

53:25.052 --> 53:28.012
- Well, all right, the offer's on the table.
- Oh, thank you.

53:28.389 --> 53:30.807
Any friend of Dad's is a friend of mine.
(CHUCKLES)

53:31.725 --> 53:35.603
(STUTTERS) How'd you know him?
Did you serve with my dad?

53:36.021 --> 53:38.898
- No.
- Well, how did you know him then?

53:40.943 --> 53:43.736
I knew him from Auschwitz.

53:47.324 --> 53:49.075
(LAUGHING)

53:49.785 --> 53:50.785
Auschwitz?

