54:14.101 --> 54:16.477
Most that the Germans
let him do was, you know,

54:16.603 --> 54:19.355
break a bunch of windows
and cook some Wiener Schnitzel, you know?

54:19.481 --> 54:22.692
I am sorry to have bothered you.

54:22.818 --> 54:27.113
- I have the wrong Rudy Kurlander.
- No, no, no. Whoa. Whoa. Whoa.

54:27.614 --> 54:30.992
Wait a minute, you were at Auschwitz?

54:31.118 --> 54:33.578
- Oh.
- None of my dad's buddies served at a camp.

54:33.704 --> 54:35.663
I must leave you now.
I have bothered you enough.

54:35.789 --> 54:37.665
Bothered me? No, no, no. Please stay.

54:37.791 --> 54:40.710
Please stay. Share some stories.

54:40.836 --> 54:42.962
I'll grab another bottle. We'll just...

54:50.137 --> 54:51.554
What's that?

54:57.102 --> 54:58.102
What is that?

54:59.646 --> 55:00.646
What the fuck is that?

55:01.815 --> 55:04.817
Well... I'm sorry. I...

55:05.611 --> 55:06.611
I, uh...

55:08.781 --> 55:09.989
What the fuck is that?

55:14.787 --> 55:15.995
Are you a Jew?

55:18.749 --> 55:19.749
Yeah.

55:21.502 --> 55:22.710
You're a Jew?

55:25.923 --> 55:27.507
What the fuck's going on here?

55:28.467 --> 55:29.675
I'm sorry, I...

55:30.511 --> 55:32.553
Sit the fuck down.

55:34.640 --> 55:36.849
Please, let me go.

55:39.686 --> 55:41.646
What the fuck are you doing in my house?

55:41.772 --> 55:45.024
I made a mistake.
Your father is the wrong man.

55:45.150 --> 55:46.442
My father?

55:49.696 --> 55:51.614
You said you were a friend of my dad.

55:53.534 --> 55:54.742
You lied to me.

55:54.868 --> 55:59.455
- I did not lie. I did not lie!
- Jesus fucking Christ.

56:02.543 --> 56:06.045
You said you were a friend of my dad,
you come into my house

56:06.630 --> 56:08.714
and you drink my fucking whiskey,

56:08.841 --> 56:11.759
and you're a dirty fucking Jew.

56:11.885 --> 56:14.011
- (EVA BARKING)
- Eva, shut the fuck up!

56:14.138 --> 56:16.556
Stop yelling!
Please, stop yelling! I will go.

56:16.682 --> 56:17.807
Sit the fuck down!

56:18.183 --> 56:20.560
You gotta answer some questions
right fucking now!

56:25.691 --> 56:28.234
Holy shit! Did you just piss on my couch?

56:29.111 --> 56:32.238
- I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.
- What the fuck?

56:32.573 --> 56:33.573
Stop yelling!

56:33.907 --> 56:35.658
- (SCREAMS)
- Eva, shut the fuck up!

56:35.784 --> 56:38.119
Are you giving me a fucking order, Jew?

56:38.245 --> 56:40.580
Eva, I said, "Shut the fuck up!"
You know...

56:41.665 --> 56:46.586
you know what my dad would say if he knew
a fucking Jew was in his house, huh?

56:46.712 --> 56:49.672
He would say, "Heil fucking Hitler."

56:49.798 --> 56:50.715
That's what he'd say. Yeah.

56:50.841 --> 56:54.802
Heil fucking Hitler!
Heil Hitler! Heil Hitler!

56:54.928 --> 56:57.054
